Package: Friedman
Title: Tools for Organizing and Visualizing Educational Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rayhan", "Khan", email = "rkhan@usf.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    This package is designed to help users organize, summarize, and visualize
    educational and workplace data in R. The package will provide functions
    for cleaning datasets, creating summary statistics, and generating simple
    visualizations for analysis and reporting.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    dplyr
License: CC0
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/rayhankhan-svg/Friedman
BugReports: https://github.com/rayhankhan-svg/Friedman/issues
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
